---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="GolfParty.io" backHref="/#work" backLabel="← Back to Work">
  <div class="mb-4">
    <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-green-200 rounded text-black">LIVE</span>
  </div>
  <img src="/images/work/golfparty.png" alt="GolfParty.io" class="w-full mb-8 rounded" />
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      A fast-paced multiplayer golf game hosted on Poki where players compete in real-time matches.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      GolfParty.io is a fast-paced multiplayer golf game that brings friends together for competitive rounds. Hosted on Poki's platform, the game features intuitive controls and dynamic courses that make each match exciting and unpredictable.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      The game combines classic golf mechanics with modern multiplayer fun, allowing players to compete in real-time matches. With smooth gameplay and engaging competitive elements, GolfParty.io offers an accessible yet challenging golf experience for players of all skill levels.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
